data.description: A very elegant home with a 3-car garage.  Four beds and 2.5 baths.  Double 8 ft, Mahogany, entry doors.  Custom Cabinets in Kitchen, stainless steel appliances, copper sinks and granite countertops.  Eat-in kitchen and a formal dining room.  Remodeled bath with large walk-in shower and walk in closet.  A large back porch deck.  Beds 2 & 3 have a Jack/Jill bath.  Tornado shelter in one of the garage bays.  Double sided gas log fireplace and woodburning fireplace in living room.  Generator to convey.  Located on 1.24 acre lot with landscaping and curb appeal.  Overhead storage in garage.  Two fruit producing trees.  The backyard has the feel of privacy and nature.
